OL,3,CGovernment launches national
OL,4,Cinvestigation into NHS maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FA national investigation into NHS
OL,8,Fmaternity services has been launched
OL,9,Fby the government following a series
OL,10,Fof maternity scandals.
OL,12,FThe new rapid investigation is
OL,13,Fintended to provide truth to families
OL,14,Fsuffering harm, as well as driving
OL,15,Furgent improvements to care and
OL,16,Fsafety, the Department for Health and
OL,17,FSocial Care (DHSC) said.
