OL,3,CGovernment launches national
OL,4,Cinvestigation into NHS maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FIt follows Health Secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting meeting families who have
OL,9,Flost babies and comes amid the ongoing
OL,10,Finvestigations at some NHS trusts into
OL,11,Fpoor maternity care.
OL,13,FIt is expected that the investigation
OL,14,Fwill report back by the end of the
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FDHSC said it is also launching a
OL,18,F"National Maternity and Neonatal
OL,19,FTaskforce", which will be chaired by
OL,20,FStreeting.
