OL,7,FThe health secretary said risk is
OL,8,F"considerably higher" than it should
OL,9,Fbe for women and babies because of a
OL,10,F"crisis" in maternity and neonatal
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the Royal College of
OL,14,FObstetricians and Gynaecologists
OL,15,F(RCOG) conference in London on Monday,
OL,16,FStreeting said bringing life carried
OL,17,Frisk but "that risk is considerably
OL,18,Fhigher than it should be because of
OL,19,Fthe state of the crisis in our
OL,20,Fmaternity and neonatal services".
