OL,7,F"Within the past 15 years, we've seen
OL,8,Fappalling scandals that blew the lid
OL,9,Fon issues ranging from care, safety,
OL,10,Fculture and oversight ` Shrewsbury,
OL,11,FTelford, East Kent, Nottingham.
OL,13,F"The last government responded with
OL,14,Finitiatives like Better Births in 2016
OL,15,Fand the maternity transformation
OL,16,Fprogramme. But despite improvements on
OL,17,Fsome metrics, inequalities in maternal
OL,18,Fand neo-natal outcomes have become
OL,19,Fmore visible, not less. The rate of
OL,20,Flate maternal deaths has been
OL,21,Fconsistently rising.
