OL,7,F"Babies of black ethnicity are twice
OL,8,Fas likely to be stillborn than babies
OL,9,Fof white ethnicity, and black women
OL,10,Fare still two to three times more
OL,11,Flikely to die during pregnancy or
OL,12,Fshortly after birth than white women.
OL,13,FTragically, that gap is closing
OL,14,Fslightly, but partly because more
OL,15,Fwhite women are dying in childbirth."
